  "description": "A long exposure night photograph showcasing a suspension bridge stretching across a body of water. The bridge is illuminated with a string of warm orange and yellow lights, creating a beautiful contrast against the dark blue of the night sky and water. The bridge appears to span a considerable distance, fading into the darkness on both sides. A faint glow of city lights is visible on the distant shoreline. The foreground features out-of-focus dark foliage, adding depth and framing the scene. There's a single bright blue light on the shore in the distance. The overall impression is one of tranquility and scale.",
